    Testing Evaluation:-
    --------------------

    This was designed with both PAL and NTSC in mind.
    An A500 in 0.5MB, 1MB and 5MB modes, a standard A500+, an A600 in 1MB,
    2MB and 6MB modes and an A1200 in 2MB, 6MB and 10MB modes.
    Workbench 1.3x to Workbench 3.0x.

